item.description:
Hi Trailblazers, join us for an evening playing the Dating Game, we will be meeting at the Friendly Toast probably in the back area.

The Dating Game is a fun way to meet others in a social nature. I don't want to spoil the excitement so you will have to trust me on playing this game, we will be going out after I spell out the rules of the game to some nightclubs and bars where we will practice the art of dating using the new rules! We will have a contest to see how many new people we can meet at the end of the evening!

Don't miss this exciting new concept for meeting people!

If you have any questions don't hesitate to contact me at:603-312-6735

Other meetup groups will be coming

Updates will be posted online if any changes.

See you there.

Peter
item.why: Awesome way to meet new people, it's a great game!
